## 🧝 Frodo the Helpful Elf – HomeAssistant Helper

**Frodo the Helpful Elf** is a HomeAssistant helper designed to motivate the little ones in your household. If a child is grumpy in the morning and doesn’t want to go to daycare, school, or kindergarten, Frodo is here to help! ✨

Every morning, 🤖 ChatGPT automatically generates funny and motivating prompts to help children get ready for the day in a fun and stress-free way. The texts are also read aloud using a 🗣️ Piper voice, so the kids can hear the motivation too. This reduces morning stress and makes starting the day more enjoyable. 🌞

### 🚀 Features

- 🤹‍♂️ Automatic, child-friendly motivation in the morning
- 🏠 Integration with HomeAssistant
- 💡 Uses ChatGPT for creative prompts
- 🔊 Generated texts are read aloud with a Piper voice
- 😌 Less stress for parents and children – brings structure to the morning

### 🎯 Target Audience

👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 Parents and families who use HomeAssistant and want to make mornings easier for their children.

